						<summary>

						<p>States that a Brahmin <hi rend="bold">Annimanchi,</hi> minister of <hi rend="bold">Tyāgi Pōta,</hi> chief of <hi rend="bold">Nātavaṭī</hi> built a Śiva temple at Animanchipaḷḷi and endowed it with lands.</p>						

